spec_data.Name: perl-DateTime-Format-Oracle
spec_data.Description:
This module may be used to convert Oracle date and timestamp values into
DateTime objects. It also can take a DateTime object and produce a date
string matching the NLS_DATE_FORMAT.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 10:56:55 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Parse and format Oracle dates and timestamps
